description:
With respect to the original scanner and those who shared that file, the quality was pretty rough. Being an incredibly huge Chris Ware nerd, I wanted to do whatever I could to improve it. I did the best I could to darken and sharpen the images, but it's still not perfect. Keep in mind, I'm an obsessive pedant about such things, so it will probably be perfectly fine for most people.

